# =========================================================
# Vera5
# IOC Enrichment Extension
# .env.example
# =========================================================
# PURPOSE:
# Example environment/config template for all supported
# enrichment providers, integrations, optional local
# services, and future expansion modules.
#
# Vera5 is BYOK/BYOA:
# (Bring Your Own Keys / Bring Your Own API)
#
# DO NOT:
# - commit real keys
# - share screenshots with live secrets
# - paste secrets into issues/discussions
#
# SAFE PRACTICES:
# - use .env locally only
# - rotate exposed keys immediately
# - apply least-privilege API scopes
#
# =========================================================
# CORE THREAT INTEL / IOC ENRICHMENT
# =========================================================

